content.html: I hope that the tech industry moves to a point where people can admit to not being geniuses, ninjas, or rockstars and have that be a positive. I hope that people can acknowledge that there is more to learn, and love that, rather than trying to one-up each other.
content.value:
I hope that the tech industry moves to a point where people can admit to not being geniuses, ninjas, or rockstars and have that be a positive.

I hope that people can acknowledge that there is more to learn, and love that, rather than trying to one-up each other.
